export const theme = Object.freeze({
    PRIMARY1: '#2AC1BC',
    PRIMARY2: '#A0E1E0',
    PRIMARY3: '#4CB8B8',
    TITLE_ACTIVE: '#1E2019',
    BODY: '#626666',
    LABEL: '#8D9393',
    PLACEHOLDER: '#C1C5C5',
    LINE: '#CCD3D3',
    BACKGROUND: '#F5F5F5',
    OFF_WHITE: '#FCFCFC',
    ERROR: '#F45452',
    LIGHT_ERROR: '#FFD4D3',
    DARK_ERROR: '#CD6766',
    DARK_GREEN: '#394032',
    WHITE: '#ffffff',
  })
  
  export type ThemeType = typeof theme
